Author: logicalq
Title: [ICO]✈️ Aircraft - Artificial Intelligence in Tourism ✈️ Softcap is reached!
Body: Website | Whitepaper | Onepager | Twitter | Facebook | Telegram  Congratulations! Softcap is reached! Despite the fall of ICO-market, at the moment we succeeded to attract more than $6,500,000 and the sum keeps raising. Stay with us! https://aircraft.travel  Referral program!      Aircraft is a blockchain based eco-system, the main mission is to expand the boundaries of cryptocurrency influence in the whole world and to ensure the availability of cryptocurrency payments. Our network is an association of high-quality specialists and companies in tourism industry. This union represents the worldwide professionals who set as primary aim to make the use of the cryptocurrency in the tourism field affordable, as well as to provide a higher level of security and quality of services in travel.  Aircraft Blockchain is designed to solve such financial and tourism problems as frauds, charge-back, overbooking, reservation mistakes and low quality of provided services. We believe that gathering, storage and updating information in one connected system will help both clients and partners of the network to avoid current problems. Aircraft aims to ensure that each transaction for each reservation and ticket is fare and no one client will be deceived. Unique platform allows to pay with more than 30 currencies, including cryptocurrencies. Special AIRT token opens doors to the world of discounts and special offers to its holders!  Features        Partners     Roadmap    ICO     Media                           FAQ  1. What is the mission of Aircraft Travel Company?  The Aircraft system sets as its primary aim to make the use of the cryptocurrency in the tourism field affordable. We believe that the future lies with technologies such as blockchain. Cryptocurrencies will be able to completely replace traditional fiat funds in 10-20 years. Despite the resistance of some countries, the adoption of cryptocurrencies as a priority means of payment gives the undeniable advantages over the usual methods of payment by cards and cash. Aircraft aims to become one of the steps of this inevitable transition to more perfect and convenient ways of payment. Everyday use of cryptocurrency as the main means of payment is not a myth, but a reality that we are building now.   2. What are advantages for clients?  Advantages for tourists are: -Aircraft is a convenient platform to find and buy the best flight, hotel and entertainment with ability of payment by cryptocurrency -Secure money settlement system that guarantee successful operations -Full protection of the personal data of the traveler -Calculation of bonus miles for spent tokens (cash-back program) -Multifunctional and thoughtful mobile application that will become an indispensable travel assistant  3. How are you going to attract partners to the Aircraft system?  Advantages for partners: -Partnership in a rapidly developing community of tourism professionals with privileges for early partners -Advertising on our platform online & offline -Attraction of customer flows, who want to pay for services using cryptocurrency -   Protection of payment data in the system -Conferences and seminars on improving the provision of services for staff  4. Can you tell about functions in your mobile application?   In Aircraft Mobile App client can:   1) Search & Buy tickets for flight 2) Book a room in the hotel 3) Book a car for rent   4) Buy tickets for events with discount 5) See recommendations for trip 6) Get inspired by watching guides and reviews 7) Deposit and withdraw funds from personal wallet 8 ) Collect and store Aircraft tokens 9) Check status in bonus programs 10) Store different cryptocurrencies: Bitcoin, Ethereum and others 11) Get access to the handy assistant - Airberry AI  5. Do you provide various payment methods?  Yes, we do. Bitcoin, Ethereum, Monero, ZCash, Ripple, Bitcoin Cash, Neo, Litecoin, DASH, EOS, Bitcoin Gold, Ethereum Classic, Verge, Stellar Lumens, IOTA, NEM, Dogecoin and others will be available on the Aircraft platform. Moreover, client can purchase using standard bank cards: Visa, MasterCard.  6. What can you tell about the Artificial Intelligence - Airberry?  Airberry is a smart AI helper in mobile app, which can answer question about future trip, announce currency rates, inform the traveler about critical situations in the country, rallies, unfavorable areas (with high crime rates), notification of mass events.  7. What are payment methods to buy tokens during the ICO?  There are two ways to buy AIRT during the stages of ICO: Bitcoin & Ethereum. You can participate in the crowdsale via dashboard on Aircraft web-site.  8 . What are terms of participation in Referral program?  You can read information about referral program and find some tips at the link: http://aircraft.travel/rewards  9. There is an item "Issue of plastic cards" in the Roadmap, how will it be implemented and what are the functions of these cards?  Payment cards will be issued in cooperation with banks that support payment by crypto currency. These cards will be given to the user upon check-in at the hotel or sent by mail (the first option preferably due to the guarantee of receiving the card by the client on time). Cards are equipped with NFC-module for instant contactless payments. Client can add the card into Apple Pay, Google Pay and Samsung Pay. On the web-site client can order a card with special design, in the mobile app after card is added, the fast exchange into necessary currency is available. Cards are working on Visa base, so payments will provide all around the world.  10. Which companies are in your list of future partners?  First of all, we are going to cooperate with companies located in countries that support crypto currency or at least do not prohibit it. We believe that, with the support of the governments, the crypto currency has every chance to take precedence in the tourist market.   Translations  Chinese Japanese Indonesian Vietnamese Filipino Arabic
